OL,3,CIran targets Israel and Gulf Arab
OL,4,Cstates as it denies talks with the US
OL,6,FSmoke rose from central Tel Aviv as
OL,7,FIranian missiles and drones targeted
OL,8,FIsrael and Gulf Arab states on
OL,9,FTuesday, even as US President Donald
OL,10,FTrump said the US was in talks with
OL,11,Fthe Islamic Republic to end the war.
OL,13,FTrump has delayed a deadline for Iran
OL,14,Fto open the strategic Strait of Hormuz
OL,15,Ffor shipping or see its power stations
OL,16,Ftargeted by airstrikes, briefly
OL,17,Fdriving down oil prices and boosting
OL,18,Fstocks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
