PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774436769
OL,3,CIran targets Israel and Gulf Arab
OL,4,Cstates as it denies talks with the US
OL,6,FThe delay offered a reprieve after the
OL,7,FUS and Iran traded threats over the
OL,8,Fweekend of strikes that could have cut
OL,9,Felectricity to millions in Iran and
OL,10,Faround the Gulf and knocked out
OL,11,Fdesalination plants that provide many
OL,12,Fdesert nations with drinking water,
OL,13,Fwhile raising fears of possible
OL,14,Fcatastrophe if nuclear plants were hit.
OL,16,FBut any information on the talks
OL,17,Fdescribed by Trump remain in dispute
OL,18,Fwith Iran , which denied any talks had
OL,19,Fbeen held.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
