OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"No negotiations have been held with
OL,12,Fthe US," Iranian parliament Speaker
OL,13,FMohammad Bagher Qalibaf posted on X,
OL,14,Fadding that "fakenews is used to
OL,15,Fmanipulate the financial and oil
OL,16,Fmarkets."
OL,18,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,19,FNetanyahu also said Israel will
OL,20,Fcontinue to strike Iran and Lebanon
OL,21,Feven as the U.S. considers a ceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
