OL,3,CIran targets Israel and Gulf Arab
OL,4,Cstates as it denies talks with the US
OL,6,F"There's more to come," he said.
OL,8,FIran fired multiple waves of missiles
OL,9,Fat Israel early on Tuesday, with
OL,10,Freports of an impact in the country's
OL,11,Fnorth, and an explosion was heard in
OL,12,Fcentral Tel Aviv, followed by
OL,13,Fbillowing smoke.
OL,15,FIn Tel Aviv, windows from multiple
OL,16,Fstories of an apartment building were
OL,17,Fblown out, and smoke came from the
OL,18,Fground floor area. It was not
OL,19,Fimmediately clear whether the damage
OL,20,Fwas caused by a missile strike or
OL,21,Fdebris from an interception.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
