OL,6,FEarlier in the day, Israel pounded
OL,7,FBeirut's southern suburbs saying that
OL,8,Fit was targeting infrastructure used
OL,9,Fby the Iran-linked Hezbollah militant
OL,10,Fgroup.
OL,12,FA strike on a residential apartment
OL,13,Fsoutheast of the Lebanese capital
OL,14,Fkilled at least two people, according
OL,15,Fto the Lebanese Health Ministry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
