OL,6,FIn Kuwait, power lines were hit from
OL,7,Fair defense shrapnel, causing partial
OL,8,Felectricity outages in several hours.
OL,9,FMissile alert sirens sounded in
OL,10,FBahrain, and Saudi Arabia's Defense
OL,11,FMinistry said it had destroyed 19
OL,12,FIranian drones targeting its oil-rich
OL,13,FEastern Province.
OL,15,FOil prices briefly fell below $100 a
OL,16,Fbarrel on Monday after Trump claimed
OL,17,Fhis government was in talks to end the
OL,18,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
