OL,6,FBut that respite was short lived, with
OL,7,Fthe price of Brent crude, the
OL,8,Finternational standard, back to $104 a
OL,9,Fbarrel in morning trading, up more
OL,10,Fthan 40% since Israel and the U.S.
OL,11,Fstarted the war on Feb. 28 .
